title: No Mario's Sky
description:
No Mario's Sky is a fan made game combining the concept of No Man's Sky with everyone's favorite Nintendo character, Mario.
This was before Nintendo filed Copyright claims since the game used Mario, Nintendo's IP. It has now been renamed DMCA's Sky to protest the DMCA Nintendo put out against them, and can be found here >>https://asmb.itch.io/dmcas-sky

This is a copy of the game before it became DMCA's Sky

Feel free to support the creators with their new game.
Also please seed this torrent for others if you can. I can't seed it forever
